9
00:01:01,187 --> 00:01:04,587
♪I'm falling♪

10
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:12,260
♪I'm waiting♪

11
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:20,262
♪Caught in doubt♪

12
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:27,620
♪Between us now♪

13
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:34,900
=Double Fugue=

14
00:01:35,147 --> 00:01:37,785
=Episode 13=

15
00:02:09,570 --> 00:02:10,370
Did something

16
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:16,410
happen that caused your panic disorder?

17
00:02:22,690 --> 00:02:25,480
If you don't want to talk,
you don't have to.

18
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:30,010
It was an accident.

19
00:02:32,010 --> 00:02:34,720
I remember pulling someone

20
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,970
out of a fire.

21
00:02:43,570 --> 00:02:45,040
Actually,

22
00:02:45,290 --> 00:02:47,130
I didn't mean to do it myself.

23
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:48,970
But that scene

24
00:02:48,970 --> 00:02:50,920
was exactly

25
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,160
like my nightmares.

26
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:54,010
I lost control and rushed in.

27
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:55,880
After saving them,

28
00:02:57,130 --> 00:02:58,370
I became like this.

29
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,410
Actually,

30
00:03:35,410 --> 00:03:36,920
the person I saved was...

31
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:38,640
Who was it?

32
00:03:41,290 --> 00:03:42,040
I...

33
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,090
I don't remember.

34
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,010
You lost

35
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:58,440
your ability to paint to save someone.

36
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,480
Do you regret it?

37
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,810
It was just an accident.

38
00:04:04,810 --> 00:04:05,850
There's nothing to regret.

39
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,130
Why do you keep staring at me?

40
00:04:27,010 --> 00:04:28,840
What's behind that black curtain?

41
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:39,880
A storage room.

42
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,010
Just some useless stuff.

43
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,810
Why do you keep staring at me?

44
00:04:57,690 --> 00:04:58,440
Sleep.

45
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,130
Lu Li.

46
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:29,080
Are you asleep?

47
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,080
No.

48
00:05:37,010 --> 00:05:38,250
I want to take you somewhere.

49
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,010
Right now?

50
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,200
Okay.

51
00:05:45,050 --> 00:05:45,610
Let's go.

52
00:06:10,697 --> 00:06:14,609
♪The first time passing by
your darkness and moonlight♪

53
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:15,520
What do you think?

54
00:06:16,730 --> 00:06:18,130
The view here is beautiful, right?

55
00:06:19,130 --> 00:06:19,920
There are birds too.

56
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,810
♪Every detail makes my world
lose its imagination♪

57
00:06:21,810 --> 00:06:22,640
Seagulls?

58
00:06:22,810 --> 00:06:29,472
♪Every stroke
carves my heartbeat on paper♪

59
00:06:29,610 --> 00:06:30,490
Do you know

60
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,080
