The way I am now

64
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,280
is unworthy to be a painter.

65
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,972
♪Every scene with you♪

66
00:06:45,110 --> 00:06:46,272
♪Is something I yearn for♪

67
00:06:46,370 --> 00:06:47,170
That's not true.

68
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:50,122
♪Red, orange, green,
blue, cyan and yellow♪

69
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:52,480
For those who create art,

70
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,880
the most important thing

71
00:06:57,490 --> 00:06:58,280
is right here.

72
00:06:58,280 --> 00:07:00,285
♪Turn rainy days to sunshine♪

73
00:07:00,572 --> 00:07:04,472
♪Seeing you sparks my imagination♪

74
00:07:04,690 --> 00:07:06,930
Skill can be developed through practice,

75
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,010
but

76
00:07:09,010 --> 00:07:10,640
the true soul of art

77
00:07:11,170 --> 00:07:12,250
lies in the heart.

78
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,520
I remember

79
00:07:16,730 --> 00:07:18,250
my mom once told me,

80
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,490
painting

81
00:07:19,490 --> 00:07:21,050
is the expression of the heart.

82
00:07:23,050 --> 00:07:23,760
Take it easy.

83
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,873
♪The first time passing by♪

84
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,050
I'll be by your side

85
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,250
as we slowly find it back.

86
00:07:28,435 --> 00:07:30,360
♪Every detail makes my world
lose its imagination♪

87
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,490
You'll be with me?

88
00:07:32,050 --> 00:07:32,520
Yes.

89
00:07:32,930 --> 00:07:34,050
I'll be with you.

90
00:07:34,335 --> 00:07:37,210
♪Every stroke♪

91
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,400
Let go of your obsession.

92
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,610
♪Carves my heartbeat on paper♪

93
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,930
Maybe one day,

94
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,080
that genius painter

95
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,250
will come back again.

96
00:07:44,250 --> 00:07:46,963
♪Yet I still can't clearly
capture your face♪

97
00:07:48,147 --> 00:07:51,972
♪Words can never reach♪

98
00:09:30,330 --> 00:09:31,130
One more time.

99
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:55,280
Who said
painting must be done with a brush?

100
00:10:09,730 --> 00:10:10,640
What do you want to do?

101
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,330
Paint.

102
00:10:14,450 --> 00:10:15,210
Paint?

103
00:10:27,735 --> 00:10:30,310
♪In the corner of the gallery♪

104
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,090
This is also considered painting.

105
00:10:34,772 --> 00:10:37,285
♪The moment you came closer♪

106
00:10:37,285 --> 00:10:39,523
♪My heart fell into silence♪

107
00:10:42,072 --> 00:10:44,235
♪Every painting♪

108
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:45,680
Try it.

109
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:47,135
♪Hid the outline of a secret♪

110
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:48,040
Me?

111
00:10:48,097 --> 00:10:50,060
♪I thought it was love♪

112
00:10:50,685 --> 00:10:53,472
♪But it was a mistake♪

113
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,090
Alright.

114
00:10:55,147 --> 00:10:58,210
♪With purpose in my heart,
I stepped into your life♪

115
00:10:58,210 --> 00:10:59,960
♪Each design♪

116
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,822
♪All for the clues♪

117
00:11:01,897 --> 00:11:03,522
♪The trust in your eyes♪

118
00:11:03,522 --> 00:11:05,385
♪Like fire on a canvas♪

119
00:11:05,672 --> 00:11:07,185
♪That burned through me♪

120
00:11:07,272 --> 00:11:10,372
♪Yet I could not escape♪

121
