♪The truth inside the gallery♪

122
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:16,635
♪Was a lie with colors fading away♪

123
00:11:16,972 --> 00:11:19,960
♪We met inside a picture frame♪

124
00:11:20,210 --> 00:11:20,970
Good job!

125
00:11:21,010 --> 00:11:23,585
♪But walked in different directions♪

126
00:11:24,572 --> 00:11:28,247
♪Every stroke was a disguise♪

127
00:11:28,385 --> 00:11:31,547
♪Every moment filled with doubt♪

128
00:11:32,422 --> 00:11:35,735
♪Love grew in the lie♪

129
00:11:35,922 --> 00:11:39,485
♪Only to be buried in the truth♪

130
00:11:39,597 --> 00:11:42,060
♪If love is an exhibition♪

131
00:11:42,197 --> 00:11:45,010
♪I'm willing to linger there forever♪

132
