♪Only to be buried in the truth♪

143
00:12:25,685 --> 00:12:28,622
♪My time in the gallery♪

144
00:12:40,090 --> 00:12:40,920
Look here.

145
00:12:42,090 --> 00:12:43,880
I think
the lighting here can be adjusted.

146
00:12:57,210 --> 00:12:57,610
Wang Jiye.

147
00:12:57,610 --> 00:12:58,560
Lu, I'm sorry.

148
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,250
Get up.

149
00:12:59,970 --> 00:13:00,920
I'm here to apologize.

150
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:01,760
Get up.

151
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,090
I... I'm here...

152
00:13:03,090 --> 00:13:03,970
Apologize? Just go.

153
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:05,440
Go.

154
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:05,560
Lu.

155
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:07,730
What are you doing?
Have you lost your mind?

156
00:13:07,730 --> 00:13:07,970
Sorry.

157
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:10,280
Lu, I'm sorry.

158
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,760
I have a big mouth.

159
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,400
I talk too much.

160
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,200
It was my fault.

161
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,010
I caused you trouble.

162
00:13:14,730 --> 00:13:16,010
Lu, I'm sorry.

163
00:13:16,010 --> 00:13:16,680
What is this?

164
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:17,610
I caused you trouble.

165
00:13:17,610 --> 00:13:18,130
Really.

166
00:13:18,130 --> 00:13:19,090
Forgive me.

167
00:13:19,370 --> 00:13:20,210
What is

168
00:13:20,210 --> 00:13:20,680
all this?

169
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:21,800
I'm begging for forgiveness.

170
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,970
Lao Wang, are you...

171
00:13:22,970 --> 00:13:24,010
What are you doing?

172
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:29,450
Nothing.

173
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:30,730
I...

174
00:13:42,610 --> 00:13:44,330
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

175
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:52,280
Save the apology for later.

176
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:55,280
The only thing we need to do now

177
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:57,130
is deny all the rumors.

178
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:58,520
Deny everything.

179
00:13:58,730 --> 00:14:00,400
But with Lu's illness,
he really can't...

180
00:14:01,210 --> 00:14:03,330
The worst thing you can do in business
is show fear.

181
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,920
The more you show,
the more they exploit it.

182
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:16,280
Lu Li.

183
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:19,330
You have to trust me.

184
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,370
Release the statement.

185
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:37,700
(Shilun Gallery Official Statement:
Online Rumors about L are False)

186
00:14:44,210 --> 00:14:45,680
Yuebai is still young.

187
00:14:46,010 --> 00:14:47,610
She's bound to be immature.

188
00:14:48,330 --> 00:14:49,730
Give her more time.

189
00:14:54,090 --> 00:14:54,880
She

190
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:56,850
is just blinded

191
00:14:56,850 --> 00:14:57,920
by romance.

192
00:14:59,130 --> 00:14:59,970
How about

193
00:15:00,490 --> 00:15:02,490
we invite both of them over this weekend

194
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:03,920
and ask them face to face?

195
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,730
This concerns the company.

196
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:06,680
We can't be careless.

197
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,520
You can arrange it.

198
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:55,610
How did it go?

199
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:01,160
Right after the statement was released,

200
00:16:01,610 --> 00:16:02,880
Su Shilun eagerly

201
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:03,970
message me.

202
00:16:04,490 --> 00:16:05,920
He wants us to go back this weekend

203
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:07,330
for a family dinner.

204
00:16:09,490 --> 00:16:11,010
Let me see.

205
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:13,610
This isn't a family dinner.

206
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:15,280
This is clearly a trap!

207
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,090
Are we going?

208
00:16:20,330 --> 00:16:21,130
Of course.

209
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:22,680
Of course we're going.

210
00:16:23,490 --> 00:16:25,330
The stage is ready.

211
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:26,610
It'd be a shame not to go.

212
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:29,210
I'll get changed then.

213
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:48,160
Ms. Qin,

214
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:48,970
you're here.

215
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:58,970
You two are finally here.

216
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,330
Your father talks about you daily.

217
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:19,560
What's the meaning of this?

218
00:17:20,970 --> 00:17:22,520
Did I do something wrong?

219
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:24,890
Well played.

220
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:26,730
You used others to do your dirty work.

221
00:17:30,970 --> 00:17:32,410
Using others

222
00:17:32,410 --> 00:17:33,560
to do my dirty work?

223
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:38,520
You gave me Su Baoyan's weakness

224
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:40,760
and made her leave the country

225
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:41,930
without blood spilled.

226
00:17:42,970 --> 00:17:44,120
You're really good.

227
00:17:49,210 --> 00:17:50,210
Look at you.

228
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:52,210
Spending too much time with artists

229
00:17:52,210 --> 00:17:53,930
makes your imagination wild.

230
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,520
The one who embezzled

231
00:17:59,320 --> 00:18:00,120
wasn't her.

232
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:02,410
It was you.

233
00:18:08,410 --> 00:18:10,210
Aren't you afraid I'll tell Su Shilun?

234
00:18:12,760 --> 00:18:14,690
Try me.

235
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:30,760
You're all here.

236
00:18:33,690 --> 00:18:34,890
Let's reintroduce ourselves.

237
00:18:36,080 --> 00:18:37,410
Mr. L.

238
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:39,320
Pleasure to meet you.

239
00:18:39,320 --> 00:18:39,930
Mr. Su.

240
00:18:39,930 --> 00:18:41,080
It's my pleasure.

241
00:18:41,320 --> 00:18:42,210
It's mine.

242
00:18:42,320 --> 00:18:43,120
Please sit.

243
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:46,690
Father.

244
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,210
Here's the thing.

245
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:58,320
We invited you today

246
00:18:58,690 --> 00:18:59,930
mainly to ask one thing.

247
00:19:01,560 --> 00:19:02,210
Lu Li.

248
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:04,520
What exactly happened to you?

249
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:06,730
How come you can't paint anymore

250
00:19:06,730 --> 00:19:07,970
at such a young age?

251
00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:10,010
Isn't that

252
00:19:10,650 --> 00:19:12,120
unfair to Yuebai?

253
00:19:14,410 --> 00:19:15,690
Only the people in the family

254
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:17,930
know what it's really like.

255
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:18,690
Yuebai.

256
00:19:19,520 --> 00:19:21,120
Listen to your tone.

257
00:19:21,490 --> 00:19:22,280
Forget it.

258
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:24,800
It's a good thing

259
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:25,890
that they get along.

260
00:19:31,170 --> 00:19:31,970
Lu Li.

261
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:36,170
Following up on Yayin's question.

262
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:37,560
I'm curious too.

263
00:19:38,320 --> 00:19:39,890
Your hands seem fine.

264
00:19:40,250 --> 00:19:41,890
Why can't you paint anymore?

265
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:42,730
Father.

266
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:45,970
The statement says it clearly.

267
00:19:46,210 --> 00:19:47,690
If you didn't understand it,

268
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:49,490
I'll read it to you again.

269
00:19:50,890 --> 00:19:51,760
Yuebai.

270
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:53,760
That's no way to speak to your dad.

271
00:19:54,560 --> 00:19:56,170
He's just concerned about you two.

272
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:58,210
If there's any problem,

273
00:19:58,210 --> 00:19:59,450
just tell us.

274
00:19:59,450 --> 00:20:00,690
We're a family.

275
00:20:00,690 --> 00:20:02,010
We can face it together.

276
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:07,320
Anyway,

277
00:20:08,170 --> 00:20:09,760
renewing the contract with Mr. Zhu

278
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:11,120
is crucial to our company.

279
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:12,800
If you can't close the deal,

280
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:15,010
don't bother with the gallery.

281
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:16,490
Father.

282
00:20:17,010 --> 00:20:18,120
Let's make a bet.

283
00:20:20,930 --> 00:20:21,890
If I fail,

284
00:20:22,210 --> 00:20:23,490
I'll leave the gallery.

285
00:20:24,280 --> 00:20:25,600
If I succeed...

286
00:20:26,890 --> 00:20:27,890
What do you want?

287
00:20:28,410 --> 00:20:30,120
I want a seat on the board.

288
00:20:40,210 --> 00:20:41,010
Deal.

289
00:20:44,320 --> 00:20:45,320
Deal.

290
00:20:48,490 --> 00:20:49,690
Enough about work.

291
00:20:50,210 --> 00:20:51,360
